{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/place-items-in-grid-areas-using-the-grid-area-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"css-grid","demoType":null,"title":"Postavite elemente u mrežne zone koristeći svojstvo grid-area","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Nakon kreiranja šablona područja za vaš alat u mrežici, kao što je prikazano u prethodnom izazovu, možete postaviti element u vaše specifično područje referenciranjem imena koje ste dodelili. Da biste to uradili, koristite atribut <code>grid-area</code> na elementu na ovaj način:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-css\">.item1 {\r\n  grid-area: header;\r\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo omogućava mreži da zna da želiš klasu objekata <code>item1</code> da bude u području koje ima ime <code>header</code>. U ovom slučaju, element će zauzeti ceo gornji red jer je taj ceo red dobio naziv područja <code>header</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5a94fe1369fb03452672e45d","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Postavi element sa klasom <code>item5</code> u područje <code>footer</code> koristeći atribut <code>grid-area</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/p/pByETK/cRrqmtV","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301132,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/place-items-in-grid-areas-using-the-grid-area-property"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item1 {\r\n    background: LightSkyBlue;\r\n  }\r\n  .item2 {\r\n    background: LightSalmon;\r\n  }\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    background: PaleTurquoise;\r\n  }\r\n  .item4 {\r\n    background: LightPink;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .item5 {\r\n    background: PaleGreen;\r\n    /* Only change code below this line */\r\n\r\n    \r\n    /* Only change code above this line */\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .container {\r\n    font-size: 40px;\r\n    min-height: 300px;\r\n    width: 100%;\r\n    background: LightGray;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;\r\n    grid-gap: 10px;\r\n    grid-template-areas:\r\n      'header header header'\r\n      'advert content content'\r\n      'footer footer footer';\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n  <div class=\"item1\">1</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item2\">2</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item3\">3</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item4\">4</div>\r\n  <div class=\"item5\">5</div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Klasa objekata <code>item5</code> bi trebalo da ima svojstvo <code>grid-area</code> sa vrednošću <code>footer</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(\r\n  __helpers.removeCssComments(code),\r\n  /.item5\\s*?{[\\s\\S]*grid-area\\s*?:\\s*?footer\\s*?;[\\s\\S]*}/gi\r\n);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#css-grid","dashedName":"place-items-in-grid-areas-using-the-grid-area-property","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"css-grid","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/use-grid-area-without-creating-an-areas-template","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/css-grid/divide-the-grid-into-an-area-template","id":"5a94fe1369fb03452672e45d","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\r\n  .item3 {\r\n    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;\r\n    display: grid;\r\n  }\r\n</s